Let’s account for the translation btw. the origins of {A}\{A\} and {B}\{B\}.
Since the axes {V}\{V\} and {A}\{A\} are parallel, we can add (xaya)=(xvyv)+(xy)=[cθ−sθsθcθ](xbyb)+(xy)=[cθ−sθxsθcθy](xbyb1)
\begin{aligned}
\begin{pmatrix}
