Given 𝐑\bm{R}, find: θ\theta and 𝐤\bm{k}

θ=arccos(12(tr𝐑−1)),𝐤=12sinθ(r32−r23r13−r31r21−r12) or 𝐤̂=12sinθ(𝐑−𝐑⊤). 
