\end{bmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
x_b \\ y_b \\ z_b \\ 1
\end{pmatrix}

If points are represented by homogeneous coordinate vectors, then A𝐩=[A𝐑B𝐭01×31]B𝐩=A𝐓BB𝐩. {^A}\bm{p} = 
\begin{bmatrix}
{^A}\bm{R}_B & \bm{t} \\ \bm{0}_{1 \times 3} & 1
