The matrix A𝐓B{^A}\bm{T}_B has a very specific structure and belongs to the special Euclidean group of dimension 33 or 𝐓∈𝐒𝐄(3)⊆ℝ4×4\bm{T} \in \bm{SE}(3) \subseteq \mathbb{R}^{4 \times 4}.









